00:27:42,731 --> 00:27:45,164
<font color="#00ffff">Aku tidak mengerti.

541
00:27:45,166 --> 00:27:48,067
<font color="#00ffff">Jesse sudah jauh lebih baik.

542
00:27:48,069 --> 00:27:49,335
<font color="#00ffff">Aku tahu.

