552
00:28:15,861 --> 00:28:18,664
<font color="#00ffff">Aku akan menemani Frankie.

553
00:28:21,834 --> 00:28:24,102
<font color="#00ffff">Aku tak bermaksud mengganggu.

554
00:28:24,104 --> 00:28:28,306
<font color="#00ffff">Aku hanya ingin memberitahumu betapa
