555
00:28:25,506 --> 00:28:28,306

556
00:28:28,308 --> 00:28:29,808
<font color="#00ffff">Apa yang kau lakukan disini?

557
00:28:29,810 --> 00:28:31,342
<font color="#00ffff">Jesse dan aku berteman.

558
00:28:31,344 --> 00:28:32,777
<font color="#00ffff">Oh, sungguh?

559
00:28:32,779 --> 00:28:34,745
<font color="#00ffff">Lalu kenapa aku tidak mengenalmu?

