638
00:34:27,922 --> 00:34:29,989
Yeah, tapi apa?

639
00:34:36,363 --> 00:34:38,897
Apa anak-anak sudah
selesai dengan servernya?

640
00:34:38,899 --> 00:34:41,267
- Kita hampir sampai.
- Beberapa menit lagi.

641
00:34:41,269 --> 00:34:44,736
Aku hanya perlu menumpang kemari sebentar.

642
00:34:44,738 --> 00:34:47,306
Rasanya mulai bau seperti
orang dibelakang sana. 

643
00:34:53,813 --> 00:34:56,505
<i>SELAMAT DATANG DI
NEW JERSEY

